tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE rental_properties (
    property_id INT NOT NULL,
    property_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    property_address TEXT NOT NULL,
    average_rating FLOAT NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (property_id)
);

CREATE TABLE tenant_reviews (
    review_id INT NOT NULL,
    property_id INT NOT NULL,
    tenant_id INT NOT NULL,
    review_text TEXT NOT NULL,
    rating INT NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (review_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES rental_properties(property_id)
);

CREATE TABLE rental_properties ( 
    property_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    property_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    property_type VARCHAR(50), 
    address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
    rating FLOAT DEFAULT 0.0 
);

CREATE TABLE reviews ( 
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    tenant_id INT REFERENCES tenants(tenant_id), 
    property_id INT REFERENCES rental_properties(property_id), 
    rating FLOAT NOT NULL, 
    comment TEXT 
);

CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT REFERENCES rental_properties(property_id),
    tenant_id INT REFERENCES tenants(tenant_id),
    rating INT NOT NULL,
    feedback TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ratings (
   rating_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id UUID,
   tenant_id UUID,
   rating_value INT NOT NULL,
   feedback TEXT,
   FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES rental_properties(property_id),
   FOREIGN KEY (tenant_id) REFERENCES tenants(tenant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE reviews (
   review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id UUID,
   tenant_id UUID,
   review_text TEXT,
   review_date DATE,
   FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES rental_properties(property_id),
   FOREIGN KEY (tenant_id) REFERENCES tenants(tenant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE average_ratings (
   average_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id UUID,
   average_rating DECIMAL(3, 2),
   num_reviews INT,
   FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES rental_properties(property_id)
);
